Class BaseWidget

BaseWidget
Direct Known Subclasses:
FooterNav, ImageThumbnailTable, InfoTable, NavTable, TextNav, TreeNav
public class BaseWidget

this is the base widget class, that all widgets are based off of. It provides some basic members and methods

$_image_dir

the root page to the images dir. This is used for any refrences to images used by this class. namely spacer.gif.

$_css_dir

private unknown $_css_dir
The path to the location of the css needed to properly render this class these are based off of the widget dir from which the libs live in.

$_css_colors

private unknown $_css_colors
Array to hold the css customizable colors for themeing. Each widget will have its own set of customizable css colors with defaults. the user can programatically modify the colors by setting them in this array.

Default Value: array()
